ji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36eedcd0c0f3ca37b8a210404c77f0629ffece42","tid":445860,"uid":124899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T23:03:12.000Z","msg":"自私既人最有缺陷"},{"pid":"3b9672f38327c58bf90a607ca0eeef4ee3a436e8","tid":445860,"uid":70205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T23:07:46.000Z","msg":"唔係，會有突變"},{"pid":"bb4ad0c587a1542e3475f61aa6a9a0da57797f4a","tid":445860,"uid":70205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T23:08:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自私既人最有缺陷</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n世上有邊個唔自私？"}]}